    Package Description
    interfaces
    public interfaces for defining the model of how the keywordProvider works with keywords, logging, and Excel workbooks.

    touchKeywords package contains all concrete classes for Touch Action Keywords that implement the IKeyword interface and extend the TouchKeyword abstract class
